(:action SliceObject

(:action get
        :parameters (?a - agent ?obj - object ?loc - location)
        :precondition (and
            (atLocation ?a ?loc)
            (inReceptacle ?obj ?loc)
        )
        and
        (holds ?a ?outO)
        (not (holdsAnyReceptacleObject ?a))
        (forall
            (?o - object)
            (when
                (inReceptacle ?o ?obj)
                (or
                    (not (holds ?a ?o))
                    (not
                        (exists (?ot - otype)
                            (and
                                (objectType ?o ?ot)
                                (isReceptacleObject ?ot)
                            )
                        )
                    )
                )
            )

        :effect (and
            (not (inReceptacle ?obj ?loc))
            (holds ?a ?obj)
        )
    )
